{"tid":1017941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"灣仔外籍漢墮樓亡　多條巴士線需改道行駛","createTime":"2019-02-11T23:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T03:56:19.000Z","uid":41404,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"779034a7b82b9943e8034086b61d86d8b10a81cd","tid":1017941,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T23:26:06.000Z","msg":"一名外籍男子凌晨4時許，在灣仔軒尼詩道239號一座大廈，從天台墮樓，當場證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署表示受事件影響，軒尼詩道向銅鑼灣方向，介乎菲林明道與史釗域道全線，以及往金鐘方向近軒尼詩道官立小學的快線，需要封閉，多條巴士線需要改道行駛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1442398-20190212.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1442398-20190212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=ac4a7531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1442398-20190212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ad79d025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1442398-20190212.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e85b534adb506f6242d474e9a0768b60a18f0cb1","tid":1017941,"uid":216642,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T23:26:54.000Z","msg":"鬼佬都頂唔住劏房？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa83dfbc756ebb5c1c0c9a4ba011f80cce06e3c7","tid":1017941,"uid":4285,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T23:26:55.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦冚家鏟"},{"pid":"13491e4de712470bce91a9a3efee0385ad65bb4f","tid":1017941,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T23:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f50c20633e942bae9f0e7a8502df16671fad34","tid":1017941,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T23:29:38.000Z","msg":"九巴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12/02<br />\n<br />\n05:40 軒尼詩道東行過菲林明道後發生事故，東行全封。路線 N1 8 2, N 3 6 8, N 6 8 0, N 6 8 1, N 6 9 1, 1 0 3, 6 0 1, 6 0 3, 6 1 9, 6 7 3, 6 8 0, 6 8 1, 6  9 0(往九龍/新界方)及9 1 4, 9 4 8, 9 4 8 A, 9 4 8 B, 9 4 8 P, 9 4 8 X, 9 6 8, 9 6 8 A(香港島方向)需改路：<br />\n<br />\n駛至軒尼詩道改左轉菲林明道，經菲林明道天橋調頭、左轉駱克道、右轉杜老誌道、左轉軒尼詩道原路，臨時取消史釗域道站，沒有加站。"},{"pid":"1add219206865cc9bb279068fc561e7c7a50dae2","tid":1017941,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"779034a7b82b9943e8034086b61d86d8b10a81cd","tid":1017941,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T23:26:06.000Z","msg":"一名外籍男子凌晨4時許，在灣仔軒尼詩道239號一座大廈，從天台墮樓，當場證實死亡。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署表示受事件影響，軒尼詩道向銅鑼灣方向，介乎菲林明道與史釗域道全線，以及往金鐘方向近軒尼詩道官立小學的快線，需要封閉，多條巴士線需要改道行駛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1442398-20190212.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1442398-20190212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=ac4a7531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1442398-20190212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ad79d025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1442398-20190212.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T23:39:09.000Z","msg":"啱啱962經過見撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8207599d787c320d95a49d395873539b40b5c84b","tid":1017941,"uid":232185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T23:39:26.000Z","msg":"都幾高下喎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wPu0pPe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwPu0pPe.png&h=269845fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddcfee7649e5d6f6d6e96b04763c74b5391d952c","tid":1017941,"uid":19287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T23:41:48.000Z","msg":"蘋果影到成地腦漿"},{"pid":"779072fe8b548c2c554afba8b002a332b93